Package game.dinosaurs

Enum Class DinoEncyclopedia

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DinoEncyclopedia>
game.dinosaurs.DinoEncyclopedia
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<DinoEncyclopedia>, Constable
public enum DinoEncyclopedia extends Enum<DinoEncyclopedia>
Enum class used to store all constants for dinosaur attributes, mainly utilized by DinoActor. The purpose of this class is to have a standardized set of values that can be accessed by other classes we needed. This ensures a single point of change, making code more maintainable.
